{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd4e87b6d6","title":"水调歌头·重上井冈山","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a87a73970a","index":0,"year":1965,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"725e249244","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄洋界，井冈山五大哨口之一，另四个是八面山、双马石、朱砂冲、桐木岭。"},{"id":"43b9350825","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"三十八年过去，弹指一挥间，从1927年10月毛泽东率领秋收起义部队上井冈山，到这次重来，已经过去了38年，他却觉得只是弹一下指、挥一下手的短时间。"},{"id":"97406c7421","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"九天揽月，九天，天的极高处。《孙子·形》：“善攻者，动于九天之上。”揽月，摘取月亮。唐李白《宣州谢跳楼钱别校书叔云》：“俱怀逸兴壮思飞，欲上青天览明月。览同揽。"},{"id":"ff8181eb33","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"捉整，喻拿敌人。元康进之《李述负荆》第四折：“管教他中捉整，手到拿来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b503cdda73","type":"title","text":"水调歌头·重上井冈山","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"725e249244","type":"paragraph","text":"久有凌云志，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"43b9350825","type":"paragraph","text":"重上并风山。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"97406c7421","type":"paragraph","text":"千里来寻故地，","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"ff8181eb33","type":"paragraph","text":"旧貌变新颜。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"fc61f4eb95","type":"paragraph","text":"到处莺歌燕舞，","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"ebef00c22c","type":"paragraph","text":"更有流水，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"01f7616eb2","type":"paragraph","text":"高路入云端。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"abbbcbb5a3","type":"paragraph","text":"过了黄洋界以，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"eea231ce02","type":"paragraph","text":"险处不须看。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"92cd87723a","type":"paragraph","text":"风雷动，","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"e65e91bf11","type":"paragraph","text":"族旗奋，","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"279df230d2","type":"paragraph","text":"是人衰。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"6134f7ab9b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]重上井冈山，1965年5月下旬，毛泽东重上井冈山游览视察。22日，先后到黄洋界和茨坪。在茨坪居住期间，了解井冈山地区水利、公路建设和人民生活，会见了老红军、烈士家属、机关干部和群众。25日写了这首词。29日下山。三十八年过去，","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"b98e9e09d5","type":"subtitle","text":"弹指一挥间。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"},{"id":"a76d375aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"可上九天揽月以，可下五洋捉整以，谈笑凯歌还。世上无难事，只要肯登攀。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6"}],"page":{"id":"701d893104","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"dd4e87b6d6","start":49,"end":50}}}},"__N_SSG":true}